      • getClosestLevelForCode

        PCMMAggregationLevel getClosestLevelForCode(PCMMSpecification configuration,
                                            List<PCMMLevel> levels,
                                            int code)
        Parameters:
        configuration - the pcmm specification
        levels - the pcmm levels
        code - the level code
        Returns:
        in the list of levels of the subelement, return the first level that code equals the code parameter. If there is no level that equals the code parameter, return the first level smallest than the code parameter.
